### Debug env
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/debug/env
Accept: application/json


### List users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/usuarios
Accept: application/json


### List clients
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/clientes
Accept: application/json


### List barbers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/barbeiros
Accept: application/json


### List services
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/services
Accept: application/json


### Create service
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste Serviço",
  "price": 29.90,
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "isActive": true
}


### List appointments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments
Accept: application/json


### Create appointment (adjust ids/time)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barberId": 1,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "clientId": 1,
  "startTime": "2030-01-01T13:00:00Z"
}


### List working hours
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/working_hours
Accept: application/json


### Create working hour
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/working_hours
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barberId": 1,
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "18:00:00"
}


### List blocked slots
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blocked_slots
Accept: application/json


### Create blocked slot
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blocked_slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barberId": 1,
  "startTime": "2030-01-01T15:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2030-01-01T16:00:00Z",
  "reason": "Maintenance"
}


